---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Ancient Gnomics">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/applications/">Applications</a> / Ancient Gnomics</div>
      <h1>Ancient Gnomics</h1>
      <p>Recovery and analysis of degraded gnome DNA from archaeological specimens.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <section>
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <div class="cards mb-2">
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🏺</div><h3>Museum Specimens</h3><p>Non-destructive DNA extraction from preserved gnome artefacts and remains.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🧊</div><h3>CryoGnome Libraries</h3><p>Specialised library prep for ultra-low input and highly fragmented gnome DNA.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🌍</div><h3>Population Gnomics</h3><p>Reconstruct historical gnome population dynamics and migration routes.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🦴</div><h3>Palaeognomics</h3><p>Recover gnome sequences from fossil material up to 800,000 years old.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-info">
        Ready to start an ancient gnomics project? <a href="/platform/">Access the platform →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
